Let me put things away here.

862
01:17:22,150 --> 01:17:25,244
<i>Micro Chip Logic,
The Liberation of the Left Brain.</i>

863
01:17:25,320 --> 01:17:29,757
- Science fiction fan, huh?
- No, that's a textbook. Computers.

864
01:17:29,825 --> 01:17:32,623
- Do you really read this stuff?
- I wrote it.

865
01:17:32,728 --> 01:17:34,889
Oh, my goodness, so you did.

866
01:17:34,963 --> 01:17:38,091
I'll tell you what, we'll put this away,
